Alembic migrations for Semper Safe.

Run from the backend/ directory:

  # Create new migration after editing db/models.py:
  alembic revision --autogenerate -m "short description"

  # Apply pending migrations to the DB:
  alembic upgrade head

  # Roll back one migration:
  alembic downgrade -1

DATABASE_URL must be set in the environment. env.py reuses
db.session._normalize_db_url so any provider's URL works.
